# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:41
translate spanish hwb_s28_90f55e85:

    # "Marina waltzes into the diner, keeping the door open for me as we scurry in from the breezy entryway."
    "Marina entra bailando al restaurante, manteniendo la puerta abierta para mí mientras nos apresuramos a entrar desde la entrada ventosa."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:43
translate spanish hwb_s28_b30657c9:

    # "Immediately, she’s drawn to the claw machine in the corner, filled to the brim with non-specific and unlicensed stuffed animals."
    "Inmediatamente, se siente atraída por la máquina de garra en la esquina, llena hasta el tope de peluches genéricos y sin licencia."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:48
translate spanish hwb_s28_191a80e5:

    # "Her eyes glitter as she tries to get me to notice the glass box of wonders."
    "Sus ojos brillan mientras intenta que note la caja de vidrio de maravillas."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:53
translate spanish hwb_s28_12b1517d:

    # "Coming from anyone else, this action would be subtle, maybe a few quick glances at most."
    "Viniendo de cualquier otra persona, esta acción sería sutil, quizás un par de miradas rápidas como máximo."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:55
translate spanish hwb_s28_404bf3ec:

    # "Coming from Marina—not so much. Instead, she repeatedly swings her head in the direction of the machine, like she’s trying to form a giant crescent moon with her neck."
    "Viniendo de Marina, no tanto. En cambio, gira la cabeza repetidamente hacia la máquina, como si intentara formar una luna creciente gigante con su cuello."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:57
translate spanish hwb_s28_50b9d38d:

    # "But I know Marina well enough now. Well enough to know {i}exactly{/i} which one she wants."
    "Pero ya conozco lo suficiente a Marina. Lo suficiente para saber {i}exactamente{/i} cuál quiere."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:59
translate spanish hwb_s28_cf3d00cb:

    # "Snuggled tight between a fuzzy ball with googly eyes and a lion with a crown lies the holy grail."
    "Acurrucado entre una bola peluda con ojos saltones y un león con corona yace el santo grial."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:61
translate spanish hwb_s28_950b7f22:

    # "A gray wolf with a polka-dot bowtie."
    "Un lobo gris con una pajarita de lunares."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:63
translate spanish hwb_s28_cfddfead:

    # "Unfortunately for her, our waitress is already waving us over to our seats. Marina stares into the glass, her foggy reflection lining up with the wolf."
    "Desafortunadamente para ella, nuestra mesera ya nos está llamando para que nos sentemos. Marina mira fijamente el vidrio, su reflejo empañado alineándose con el lobo."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:65
translate spanish hwb_s28_5c2e5707:

    # "I take her hand and lead her to the booth. Once there’s some distance between us and the waitress, I lower my voice."
    "Tomo su mano y la llevo a la cabina. Una vez que hay algo de distancia entre nosotras y la mesera, bajo la voz."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:69
translate spanish hwb_s28_87695899:

    # Amber "Don’t worry. I’ll give it a whirl after we eat."
    Amber "Не переживай, я попробую после того как мы поедим."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:71
translate spanish hwb_s28_9d631e96:

    # "Marina, however, can’t take a hint, and blurts out her response, alerting every weary soul in the diner."
    "Marina, sin embargo, no capta la indirecta y suelta su respuesta, alertando a cada alma cansada en el restaurante."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:75
translate spanish hwb_s28_02860e8f:

    # Marina "Woah! You actually know how to win at those? I've never been any good at them."
    Marina "Вау! Ты правда умеешь их вытаскивать?! У меня никогда в жизни не получалось."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:77
translate spanish hwb_s28_75de7b5f:

    # "A counter lined with Jumbo clones turns around and glares at us before shaking their heads and returning to their meals."
    "Una fila de clones de Jumbo se da la vuelta y nos fulmina con la mirada antes de negar con la cabeza y volver a sus comidas."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:81
translate spanish hwb_s28_2521d867:

    # "Oh well."
    "Bueno, qué más da."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:85
translate spanish hwb_s28_07487736:

    # Amber "Of course I do. You know how many of these diners I went to as a kid?"
    Amber "Конечно, умею. Я в миллион таких кафе ходила ребенком."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:89
translate spanish hwb_s28_6124a02c:

    # Amber "When you eat at the same place almost every day, you get good. Fast."
    Amber "Походи в подобные места почаще и станешь профи. Причем довольно быстро."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:93
translate spanish hwb_s28_9d874f69:

    # Marina "Wow… you’re like a claw goddess."
    Marina "Вау, так ты у нас, выходит, “богиня Клешни”?"

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:97
translate spanish hwb_s28_d0b22b8e:

    # Amber "Damn right."
    Amber "Да, черт возьми."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:105
translate spanish hwb_s28_3fa8dd00:

    # "Marina ogles me like the ‘claw goddess’ I am as we take our seats at the booth. I gladly accept her glory and praise."
    "Marina me mira con admiración como la 'diosa de la garra' que soy mientras nos sentamos en la cabina. Acepto con gusto su gloria y alabanza."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:107
translate spanish hwb_s28_ec717ae9:

    # "The waitress flops the menus on our table and silently waits for us to order our drinks."
    "La mesera deja caer los menús en nuestra mesa y espera en silencio a que pidamos nuestras bebidas."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:111
translate spanish hwb_s28_5b3bfa5a:

    # Amber "Just coffee for me."
    Amber "Мне только кофе."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:113
translate spanish hwb_s28_82549954:

    # "With her eyes glazing over, she turns to Marina."
    "Con los ojos vidriosos, se vuelve hacia Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:117
translate spanish hwb_s28_2b86f185:

    # Marina "Hmm. What kinda shakes do you have?"
    Marina "Хмм. А какие шейки у вас есть?"

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:119
translate spanish hwb_s28_90e9481d:

    # "The waitress reaches her wrinkly hands across the table and tosses the dessert menu in front of Marina."
    "La mesera extiende sus manos arrugadas sobre la mesa y deja caer el menú de postres frente a Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:123
translate spanish hwb_s28_b6d2a606:

    # Marina "Hmmmmmmmmm."
    Marina "Хммммммммм."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:125
translate spanish hwb_s28_bf2a1420:

    # "She flips through the menus and strains her eyes shut, focusing on what very well may be the most important decision of her life."
    "Hojea los menús y cierra los ojos con esfuerzo, concentrándose en lo que bien podría ser la decisión más importante de su vida."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:129
translate spanish hwb_s28_834be6bf:

    # Marina "Amber, you got coffee, right?"
    Marina "Эмбер, ты ведь кофе заказала, так?"

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:131
translate spanish hwb_s28_f11d52dc:

    # Amber "Right."
    Amber "Так."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:135
translate spanish hwb_s28_598155c3:

    # Marina "Then that’s what I’ll get!"
    Marina "Тогда я вот что возьму!"

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:137
translate spanish hwb_s28_bd505669:

    # "Overflowing with certainty, she stares at the waitress and gives her a direct, confident command."
    "Rebosante de certeza, mira fijamente a la mesera y le da una orden directa y segura."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:139
translate spanish hwb_s28_ab343046:

    # Marina "I’ll have the coffee shake."
    Marina "Мне кофейный шейк."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:141
translate spanish hwb_s28_8d0e222f:

    # Marina "Extra whipped cream."
    Marina "С дополнительными взбитыми сливками."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:143
translate spanish hwb_s28_18f19e07:

    # "The waitress doesn’t even bother to write this down, instead dragging her body back to her tomb in the kitchen."
    "La mesera ni siquiera se molesta en anotarlo, arrastrando su cuerpo de vuelta a su tumba en la cocina."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:147
translate spanish hwb_s28_aa5192cc:

    # Amber "You know that shake isn’t going to taste the same as my coffee, right? It’s just gonna be a ton of ice cream and cheap coffee flavoring."
    Amber "Ты ведь понимаешь, что этот шейк даже близко не будет похож по вкусу на мой кофе, да? Будет только куча мороженого и дешевый кофейный ароматизатор."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:151
translate spanish hwb_s28_8b587bb4:

    # Marina "Yeah…"
    Marina "Агааа..."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:155
translate spanish hwb_s28_d3ffb1ea:

    # Marina "But I at least gotta try it! For your sake!"
    Marina "Но я хотя бы попробую его! Ради твоего же блага!"

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:159
translate spanish hwb_s28_1699d336:

    # Amber "Why would you choke down a crappy shake for {i}my{/i} sake?"
    Amber "С чего бы это тебе давиться дрянным шейком ради {i}моего блага{i}?"

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:161
translate spanish hwb_s28_d8cd3c86:

    # Marina "You do everything for me. Everythiiiiing."
    Marina "Ты делаешь все для меня. Всеееееее."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:163
translate spanish hwb_s28_c7a20db1:

    # Amber "‘Course I do. That’s my job."
    Amber "Конечно, делаю. Это моя работа."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:165
translate spanish hwb_s28_08e0dd2d:

    # "A stiff chuckle slips out from under her breath."
    "Una risa forzada se escapa de entre sus labios."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:169
translate spanish hwb_s28_193a362d:

    # Marina "Right…"
    Marina "Так и есть..."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:175
translate spanish hwb_s28_6be38190:

    # Marina "But I wanna do things for you, too!"
    Marina "Ну и мне хочется для тебя что-то сделать!"

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:179
translate spanish hwb_s28_9b2f4ba5:

    # Amber "So you’re ordering the coffee shake as a cosmic favor? You’re losing me, Mare."
    Amber "И поэтому ты ради меня заказываешь кофейный шейк? Ничего не понимаю, Мари."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:181
translate spanish hwb_s28_39ccc72f:

    # "She whines, momentary frustration seeping onto her face."
    "Gimotea, dejando que la frustración momentánea se asome en su rostro."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:185
translate spanish hwb_s28_0e49e18d:

    # Marina "No, not like that."
    Marina "Нет, все не так."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:189
translate spanish hwb_s28_e1d4da6c:

    # Marina "It’s silly, but I want to poke around in your mind a little. That way I {i}can{/i} do favors and help."
    Marina "Это может показаться глупым, но мне хочется немного покопаться у тебя в голове, получше узнать и почувствовать тебя. Так я {i}смогу{i} быть тебе полезной и помогать."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:193
translate spanish hwb_s28_8c8b729b:

    # Marina "So I guess it’s not just for your sake, but for both our sakes!"
    Marina "И на самом деле, я думаю, что все это не только ради тебя, а ради нас обеих!"

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:195
translate spanish hwb_s28_6bf4e9e3:

    # "She smiles and rests her head to the side, as if expecting my shoulder to be there like always."
    "Sonríe y recuesta la cabeza hacia un lado, como si esperara que mi hombro estuviera ahí, como siempre."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:200
translate spanish hwb_s28_a2ad7cf8:

    # "Realizing she’s only leaning on air, Marina blinks, then tries to play it off with a tiny cough."
    "Al darse cuenta de que solo se apoya en el aire, Marina parpadea y luego intenta disimularlo con una pequeña tos."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:204
translate spanish hwb_s28_dd15a3d8:

    # Amber "I saaaw that."
    Amber "Я всеее видела."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:208
translate spanish hwb_s28_2638e66f:

    # "Before I can take my teasing to more exciting places, the waitress returns from the kitchen, barely managing to balance our drinks on the platter as my coffee splashes everywhere."
    "Antes de que pueda llevar mis burlas a terrenos más divertidos, la mesera regresa de la cocina, apenas logrando equilibrar nuestras bebidas en la bandeja mientras mi café se derrama por todas partes."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:210
translate spanish hwb_s28_ba76e54a:

    # "She doesn’t seem to care."
    "Parece no importarle."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:212
translate spanish hwb_s28_6b44193f:

    # "She places our drinks on the table, then limps out her notepad and pen to take our orders."
    "Coloca nuestras bebidas sobre la mesa, luego saca su libreta y pluma para tomar la orden."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:216
translate spanish hwb_s28_ef71bc42:

    # Amber "Thanks, but I’ll stick with coffee."
    Amber "Спасибо, но мне хватит и кофе."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:218
translate spanish hwb_s28_d9f7c01f:

    # "Marina is too distracted by the shake to notice. Her eyes climb up the tower of ‘extra’ whipped cream as it twirls to the ceiling, rivaling the thermometer outside."
    "Marina está demasiado distraída con el batido para notarlo. Sus ojos trepan por la torre de crema batida \"extra\" mientras gira hacia el techo, rivalizando con el termómetro de afuera."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:222
translate spanish hwb_s28_4b17e949:

    # Amber "Snap to. What do ya want?"
    Amber "Эй! Еще будешь что-нибудь?"

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:229
translate spanish hwb_s28_350456c8:

    # Marina "Oh!"
    Marina "Ох!"

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:231
translate spanish hwb_s28_78cbc107:

    # "She opens up the big menu and flips through the pages—multiple times, front to back, side-to-side, even upside, repeating the process every time."
    "Abre el menú grande y hojea las páginas—varias veces, de adelante hacia atrás, de lado a lado, incluso al revés, repitiendo el proceso cada vez."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:233
translate spanish hwb_s28_932e44c9:

    # Amber "Before we miss the festival, Mare."
    Amber "Поторопись, Мари."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:237
translate spanish hwb_s28_0057ca37:

    # Marina "I know, I know, but there’s so much to choose from! I have to be picky!"
    Marina "Ладно, ладно, но тут столько всего! Есть над чем подумать!"

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:241
translate spanish hwb_s28_c352c66c:

    # Amber "You didn’t have a problem vacuuming up everything at the buffet."
    Amber "Ты без проблем разделалась бы со всеми блюдами сразу."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:245
translate spanish hwb_s28_ffcc9627:

    # "Marina drops the menu. If it were a few pounds heavier I’m pretty sure she would have dropped it on my feet."
    "Marina deja caer el menú. Si pesara unos kilos más, estoy segura de que lo habría dejado caer sobre mis pies."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:247
translate spanish hwb_s28_b6b099be:

    # "Handing the menus to the waitress, she leans over the table, inches away from my face. She places her order, burning holes in pupils."
    "Entregando los menús a la mesera, se inclina sobre la mesa, a centímetros de mi cara. Hace su pedido, quemando agujeros en mis pupilas."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:249
translate spanish hwb_s28_d71d562d:

    # Marina "I’ll have the pancake sandwich."
    Marina "Я возьму сэндвич из блинчиков."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:251
translate spanish hwb_s28_57900f07:

    # "Dead. Serious."
    "Totalmente. Seria."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:253
translate spanish hwb_s28_24d60282:

    # "The waitress wobbles away, somehow not collapsing on her way back to the kitchen."
    "La mesera se tambalea, sin derrumbarse de camino a la cocina."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:255
translate spanish hwb_s28_1be2a5f1:

    # "I try not to burst out laughing at Marina, but it doesn’t work. The cracks are showing. Stilted snorts and spurts of snickering keep leaking out."
    "Intento no reírme a carcajadas de Marina, pero no funciona. Las grietas se notan. Resoplidos entrecortados y risitas ahogadas no dejan de escaparse."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:261
translate spanish hwb_s28_234684c8:

    # "Marina’s cheeks puff out, getting brighter as I bubble over."
    "Las mejillas de Marina se inflan, poniéndose más rojas mientras yo me deshago en risas."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:263
translate spanish hwb_s28_6734a525:

    # Marina "Why do you have to tease me about everything, Amber?"
    Marina "Зачем ты меня постоянно дразнишь, Эмбер?"

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:265
translate spanish hwb_s28_319c7714:

    # "I break. My laugh echoes across the diner. Again, we’re met with glares, but I don’t even care."
    "Me quiebro. Mi risa resuena por toda la cafetería. De nuevo, nos ganamos miradas fulminantes, pero ya no me importa."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:269
translate spanish hwb_s28_584421ec:

    # Marina "Fine! Maybe I won’t share the treasure with you after all!"
    Marina "Ну и отлично! Вообще не поделюсь с тобой сокровищами после такого!"

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:271
translate spanish hwb_s28_7612f5fa:

    # "I wave off her empty threat and settle down."
    "Desestimo su amenaza vacía con un gesto y me calmo."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:275
translate spanish hwb_s28_2d8aaed2:

    # Amber "I’m sorry, I’m sorry."
    Amber "Ну прости, прости."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:277
translate spanish hwb_s28_cb5de752:

    # Amber "It’s just that…"
    Amber "Дело в том, что..."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:279
translate spanish hwb_s28_00c18ad9:

    # "Done laughing, I rest my chin on the table and start fumbling with the salt and pepper shakers."
    "Dejando de reír, apoyo la barbilla en la mesa y empiezo a jugar con los saleros y pimenteros."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:283
translate spanish hwb_s28_705175fb:

    # Amber "That’s what Gramps used to order. {i}All{/i} the time."
    Amber "Это раньше заказывал дедушка. {i}Постоянно.{i}"

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:287
translate spanish hwb_s28_c48b91db:

    # "Marina has already reverted back to her usual self, watching me pass the salt and pepper back and forth, like she wants to join in too."
    "Marina ya ha vuelto a su ser habitual, observándome pasar el salero y el pimentero de un lado a otro, como si ella también quisiera unirse."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:289
translate spanish hwb_s28_6e1febd3:

    # Amber "It’s so weird. Just two huge pancakes with eggs, bacon, and ham smashed in the middle. Thing’s drenched in syrup."
    Amber "Так странно. Просто два больших блинчика с беконом, ветчиной, и взбитыми посередине яйцами. Залитые сиропом."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:293
translate spanish hwb_s28_b2a1703b:

    # Marina "That sounds super tasty, though!"
    Marina "Но звучит же супер вкусно!"

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:295
translate spanish hwb_s28_b7b7e153:

    # "I chuckle and slide her the pepper."
    "Me río y le deslizo el pimentero."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:297
translate spanish hwb_s28_ea926111:

    # Amber "I’m sure you’ll love it."
    Amber "Я уверена, что тебе понравится."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:299
translate spanish hwb_s28_a1d403dd:

    # "Now it’s just the salt shaker, sliding between my hands."
    "Ahora solo queda el salero, deslizándose entre mis manos."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:301
translate spanish hwb_s28_6987cc5c:

    # Amber "He never eats the eggs. Always just passes them onto me."
    Amber "Он никогда не ел яйца. Всегда отдавал их мне."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:303
translate spanish hwb_s28_de486e1e:

    # Amber "They’re so gross. Just scrambled and cold and sticky."
    Amber "Они такие мерзкие. Особенно всмятку, такие холодные и вязкие."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:305
translate spanish hwb_s28_3d0044f8:

    # Amber "I always tell him no, but the dork just laughs and says he’s gonna keep ‘{i}egg’n{/i} me on.’"
    Amber "Я всегда отказывалась, но он, гад, только ржет и говорит, что я настоящих яиц не трогала, вот и не нравятся."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:307
translate spanish hwb_s28_cdd5f6ce:

    # Amber "Every single time."
    Amber "Каждый долбаный раз."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:309
translate spanish hwb_s28_7dae6550:

    # "Marina laughs at the stupid joke. I laugh too."
    "Marina se ríe del chiste tonto. Yo también me río."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:311
translate spanish hwb_s28_b98c3d0e:

    # Amber "We would just end up bringing it home in a box. And when it went bad he would just take it out of the fridge and say ‘That’s all, yolks!’ Like it was the most clever freakin’ thing."
    Amber "В итоге мы забираем этот гоголь-моголь с собой домой в коробке. А когда тот протухает в холодильнике, дедушка вытаскивает его оттуда и говорит: “Нельзя держать все яйца в одном танцоре!” Как будто это обалдеть какая смешная шутка."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:313
translate spanish hwb_s28_f117851c:

    # "She laughs even harder at that one. I think I do too."
    "Se ríe aún más fuerte de ese. Creo que yo también."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:315
translate spanish hwb_s28_bb7c896f:

    # "I keep my eyes focused on the shaker, sliding it faster and faster."
    "Mantengo la vista fija en el salero, deslizándolo cada vez más rápido."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:317
translate spanish hwb_s28_5411baaf:

    # Amber "When we go home, you two really need to get together and me—"
    Amber "Когда приедем домой, вам бы стоило—."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:321
translate spanish hwb_s28_f41d3c87:

    # "The salt shaker trips on my pinkie and topples over, spilling a few grains of salt."
    "El salero tropieza con mi meñique y se voltea, derramando unos granos de sal."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:325
translate spanish hwb_s28_43ff4efc:

    # "Marina is tense, but forces a smile anyway."
    "Marina está tensa, pero se obliga a sonreír de todas formas."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:331
translate spanish hwb_s28_cb3d0422:

    # "She sighs. We both look down and go silent."
    "Suspira. Ambas miramos hacia abajo y nos quedamos en silencio."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:337
translate spanish hwb_s28_be6933b9:

    # Amber "I, uh—I think I’m gonna head back to the RV."
    Amber "Я, мм.. Думаю, я пойду в трейлер."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:342
translate spanish hwb_s28_19c6d5d4:

    # "I get up and reach into my pocket, placing a bill on the table."
    "Me levanto y meto la mano en el bolsillo, colocando un billete sobre la mesa."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:346
translate spanish hwb_s28_e247a094:

    # Marina "Amber—"
    Marina "Эмбер–"

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:348
translate spanish hwb_s28_08f2d431:

    # Amber "Don’t worry, I’ll be fine. Just need some time."
    Amber "Не волнуйся, все в порядке. Просто мне нужно немного времени."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:353
translate spanish hwb_s28_1a0b1d7b:

    # "Leaving Marina behind me, I walk out of the diner."
    "Dejando a Marina atrás, salgo del restaurante."

# game/script/hwb_s28.rpy:247
translate spanish hwb_s28_bc7a8980:

    # "Handing the menus to the waitress, she leans over the table, inches away from my face. She places her order. Her pupils burn with intensity."
    "Al entregar los menús a la mesera, se inclina sobre la mesa, a centímetros de mi cara. Hace su pedido. Sus pupilas arden con intensidad."

